Checklist for Making New Software Release
-----------------------------------------

Perform these steps to ensure a good distribution.

1. emacs configure.in
   Change the version number.

2. emacs README
   Change the version number + date.

3. emacs CHANGES
   Change the version number + date.

4. netscape zr.html
   Change the version number + date.

5. autoreconf

6. configure

7. make

8. make install
   This will change the version in all scripts.

9. cvs commit -m 'Ready for v1.xx'

10. make dist

11. ../to_ftp_archive build_zr_table-v1.xx.tgz

12. mv build_zr_table-v1.9.tar.gz ../gvbox/packages/

13. cvs tag v1_xx
